import "../styles/global.css";
import type { CarouselImage } from "../types/CarouselImages"
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import MeImage from "../assets/me.jpg";

---

<section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row max-w-8/10 mx-auto py-12 gap-6">
  <!-- Hero -->
	<Image src={MeImage} 
		alt="Myself and the kamakura buddha statue in the background" 
		class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-full object-cover rounded-2xl shadow"
		/>
    <aside class="w-full md:w-1/2 bg-amber-200 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Hello, my name is Brian.</h1>
	  <p>I started my journey in technology as a kid, always messing around with computers.</p>
	  <br />
	  <p>
		That passion led me to finish a bachelors 
	   	degree in Mechatronics Engineering, where I discovered a strong interest in software development. I began experimenting with 
	   	some Python scripts, online tutorials, and more.  
	  </p>
	  <br />
	   <p>
 		Later, I get my first job as SOE on a Shipping Agency. They need it someone capable of translate their
		old applications into better sofware that can help us deliver faster and safely with strong tools. It help me to gain hand-ons
		experience in real-world projects, using Python for Destkop development and NodeJS + Angular to deliver their web applications.
	   </p>
	   <br />
	   <p>
		After completing those projects, I wanted to push myself further and break away from working alone. 
	   I took the chance to attend a bootcamp in Tokyo, Japan. It was an eye-opening experience where I made lasting friendships, 
	   learned to work in teams, and developed a true passion for software development.
	   </p>
	   <br />
	   <p>Now, Im actively looking for my next opportunity, excited to contribute, learn, and keep growing as a dev, and as a person.</p>
      </p>
    </aside>
</section>

